description.p:
The invention relates to an apparatus comprising:
an envelope feeder configured to feed envelopes to a product receiving position;
a positioning structure configured to position the envelopes in said receiving position;
an inserter configured to insert products into envelopes, positioned in the receiving position, in a product inserting direction; and
an envelope conveyor to remove filled envelopes from the receiving position, in an envelope removal direction.

Further elaborations of the inserting apparatus according to the invention are described in the dependent claims and will hereinafter, together with the method according to the invention, be further elucidated with reference to the drawing.
